  "bio_raw": "Nafees Reza earned an M.Sc. in Finance from Tilburg University, Netherlands, and a Bachelor of Business Administration with a major in Finance and a minor in Accounting from Independent University, Bangladesh, graduating Magna Cum Laude. He is an experienced academic with teaching experience at Independent University, Bangladesh (IUB) and currently serves as Adjunct Faculty at University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB).\nHis research interests include equity valuation, Market volatility, and investor behavior. He has published in international journals such as the International Journal of Accounting Research and the Asian Economic and Financial Review, with additional working papers currently in progress. Alongside his academic work, he possesses strong quantitative and research skills, including proficiency in STATA, SPSS, and Excel VBA.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Equity valuation, Market volatility, and Investor behavior."
  ],
