  "publications_raw": [
    "Journal Articles\nReza, N.\n, & Quraishi, M. K. (2025). The interplay of financial report complexity: Assessing its influence on debt financing and share price. Asian Economic and Financial Review, 15(5), 670–682. https://doi.org/10.55493/5002.v15i5.5385\nReza, N.\n, & Quraishi, M. K. (2024). The effect of disclosure on investment efficiency–Evidence from the listed companies of Bangladesh. International Journal of Accounting Research, 9(2), 57-64.\nReza, N.\n, & Quraishi, M. K. (2015). Quality of Bank Audit in Bangladesh and Relationship between Audit Quality and Share Price. ELK Asia Pacific Journal of Finance and Risk Management, 6(2), 44-56."
